    <note>Cui(1) Xian [1678] His ancestors were Boling jun Cui(1). His son, Zundu [3863], moved from Jiangling, Jiangling xian to Zizhou, Zichuan xian. However, his great grandson, Zhu [3881], died in Jiangling at the age of 41. Zhu had neither a household to mourn his death nor a son to perform sacrifices. Xian's other son, Zunyong [3884], was Fan(2) Zhi's [8041] son-in-law and does not seem to have had any surviving children when he died. Xian was Su(1) Yijian's [8115] father-in-law. XCB, 19.7b; SS, 441.22a; Su Shunqin, WJ, 14.213-214; YLDD, 2744.18b. CBD, 3, 2709.</note>
